{"type":"message","id":"01224d85","parentId":"0b1aa859","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:21:31.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"由于通过浏览器逐个获取股票数据效率太低，我需要改用 Python 脚本直接调用东方财富 API 批量获取所有自选股的实时数据。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我获取到了中国石油的实时数据。从页面可以看到：\n- 代码：601857\n- 名称：中国石油\n- 当前价：11.95 元\n- 涨跌幅：-7.51%\n- 涨跌额：-0.97 元\n- 时间：2026-03-10 14:21:10\n\n由于需要获取多个股票的数据，让我使用更高效的方式 - 通过 web_fetch 获取同花顺的实时数据页面，然后编写一个脚本来批量获取所有股票数据。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_09b9e69c7db94f418e069945","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock && python3 << 'EOF'\nimport requests\nfrom datetime import datetime\nimport re\n\n# 读取 watchlist\nwith open('stock/watchlist.txt', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    lines = f.readlines()\n\nstocks = []\nfor line in lines:\n    line = line.strip()\n    if line and '|' in line:\n        code, name = line.split('|')\n        stocks.append((code, name))\n\n# 东方财富实时行情 API\nresults = []\nfor code, name in stocks:\n    try:\n        # 判断市场\n        if code.endswith('.HK'):\n            # 港股\n            secid = f\"116.{code.replace('.HK', '')}\"\n        elif code.startswith('6') or code.startswith('9'):\n            # 沪市\n            secid = f\"1.{code}\"\n        elif code.startswith('0') or code.startswith('3'):\n            # 深市\n            secid = f\"0.{code}\"\n        else:\n            # 美股等其他市场，跳过\n            results.append({\n                'code': code,\n                'name': name,\n                'price': 'N/A',\n                'change_percent': 'N/A',\n                'change': 'N/A',\n                'time': datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n            })\n            continue\n        \n        url = f\"http://push2.eastmoney.com/api/qt/stock/get?secid={secid}&fields=f43,f44,f45,f46,f47,f48,f49,f50,f51,f52,f53,f54,f55,f56,f57,f58,f59,f60,f61,f169,f170\"\n        resp = requests.get(url, timeout=5)\n        data = resp.json()\n        \n        if data.get('data'):\n            d = data['data']\n            price = d.get('f43', 0) / 100 if d.get('f43') else 0\n            change_percent = d.get('f170', 0) if d.get('f170') else 0\n            change = d.get('f44', 0) / 100 if d.get('f44') else 0\n            \n            results.append({\n                'code': code,\n                'name': name,\n                'price': f\"¥{price:.2f}\" if price else 'N/A',\n                'change_percent': f\"{change_percent:+.2f}%\" if change_percent != 0 else '0.00%',\n                'change': f\"¥{change:.2f}\" if change else 'N/A',\n                'time': datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n            })\n        else:\n            results.append({\n                'code': code,\n                'name': name,\n                'price': 'N/A',\n                'change_percent': 'N/A',\n                'change': 'N/A',\n                'time': datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n            })\n    except Exception as e:\n        results.append({\n            'code': code,\n            'name': name,\n            'price': 'N/A',\n            'change_percent': 'N/A',\n            'change': 'N/A',\n            'time': datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S'),\n            'error': str(e)\n        })\n\n# 输出结果\nprint(\"代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额 | 时间\")\nfor r in results:\n    print(f\"{r['code']} | {r['name']} | {r['price']} | {r['change_percent']} | {r['change']} | {r['time']}\")\nEOF"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773123674089}}
